creator: Henry Wadsworth Longfellow
description:
LibriVox recording of The Rainy Day by Henry Wadsworth Longfellow.
Read in English by Alan Rose; Alex Vause; Claudia Salto; CaprishaPage; Diana Majlinger; Drew Johnson; David Lawrence; DeenaMae; dsilber01; Ernst Pattynama; Garth Burton; Jason Mills; Jennifer Dorr; Jannie Meisberger; Julia Niedermaier; Lee Ann Howlett; Leonard Wilson; mlcui; Pam Castille; Ralph Crown; Richard Corfield; ravenotation; Anastasiia Solokha; Steve Lawrence; Suprada Urval

LibriVox volunteers bring you 25 recordings of The Rainy Day by Henry Wadsworth Longfellow. This was the Weekly Poetry project for September 29, 2013. (Summary by Diana Majlinger)

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

M4B Format Available
